{"tid":347500,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尼馬：加盟巴黎聖日耳門　並非為錢","createTime":"2017-08-05T01:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T08:13:51.000Z","uid":20933,"like":27,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9927c4ea255ae1ab0257868dac4cc70c8f83d4be","tid":347500,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T01:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1346463_1_20170805071018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1346463_1_20170805071018.jpg&h=b20011fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴西球星尼馬表示，加盟法甲巴黎聖日耳門，並非為錢。<br />\n<br />\n尼馬以2億2200萬歐元身價，由西甲巴塞羅拿轉投聖日耳門。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，從來不會只是為錢做事，如果單為金錢，他可以在世界很多地方，選擇其他球會作賽，加盟聖日耳門，是希望能夠與球隊一起，為球壇帶來一些改變。說他轉會只是為錢，令他傷感。"},{"pid":"6bf5a0a897b5c8a0bd765ba4397acb60877fc7d8","tid":347500,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T01:04:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1346463-20170805.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1346463-20170805.htm&d=0O233upXlWXGQUOtfKSFDUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a2bcb1a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1346463-20170805.htm&h=21b057d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1346463-20170805.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0c64afb609e232312f6e00a58ef27387c6383a16","tid":347500,"uid":99114,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T01:06:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1346463_1_20170805071018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1346463_1_20170805071018.jpg&h=b20011fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴西球星尼馬表示，加盟法甲巴黎聖日耳門，並非為錢。<br />\n<br />\n尼馬以2億2200萬歐元身價，由西甲巴塞羅拿轉投聖日耳門。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，從來不會只是為錢做事，如果單為金錢，他可以在世界很多地方，選擇其他球會作賽，加盟聖日耳門，是希望能夠與球隊一起，為